todo list webapp

features:
- has three subsections: immediate goals, short term goals, long term goals
--- immediate goals: title only, needs to be done immediately
--- short term goals: title with deadline with progress and comments
--- long term goals: title with deadline with comments
- has [all], which lists all goals
- has [archive], which lists all goals completed // omitted. unnecessary
- there is a checkbox to filter only uncompleted goals for every subsections
- there is a checkbox and date textbox to filter 

technical requirements:
- uses node js
- web
- deploy in heroku
- mongodb
- optional: angular
